Root workspace: `/opt/Axodus`

Versioning note: `/opt/Axodus` is not a Git repository. This global report and global portfolio updates are local/unversioned unless later migrated to a versioned portfolio documentation repository.

## Summary

PORTFOLIO-REQ-01 created consolidated local `.instructions/STATUS.md` files and maturity assessments for all six target nuclei. The cycle intentionally did not implement product features, did not enable production execution, and did not promote maturity from roadmap alone.

All six nuclei are conservatively documented as L3 candidates or below for comparable portfolio governance until current validation evidence is refreshed.

Portfolio cycle result: PORTFOLIO_STATUS_NORMALIZED

