## Missing Files Before Normalization

All six target nuclei were missing:

- `.instructions/STATUS.md`
- `.instructions/BLOCKER_REGISTER.md`
- `.instructions/VALIDATION.md`
- `.instructions/HANDOFF.md`

All six now have these files plus a nucleus-specific maturity assessment.

